footnotes: The variation 16zv (Reverse Bob with Reverse Gwendroc Singles) is rung for the first time. The band would like to name this variation Llanfairpwllgwyngyllgogerychwyrndrobwllllantysiliogogogoch.
Rung because early today, an inferior York band rang and named the variation we were going to ring and name.
The band would like to associate Benjamin J Hartley with this performance, who was scribbling some crazy method on the blackboard during this performance.
